==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jalousie
<hw>Ja`lou`sie"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Jealousy</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A Venetian or slatted inside
window blind.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A window or door made of multiple glass or plastic
slats, which can be opened or closed like a jalousie{1}.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jalousied</ent>⟦br⟧
